                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8594" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1311</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1651 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">慢火煎茶熟，国风助香传：林丰茶叶公司的品牌定位之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Cook the tea slowly, and use the national breeze to help the aroma of the tea go further：Linfeng tea Company&#39;s brand positioning road</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">周宇飞，朱睿，周文定，田佳丽</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖南农业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张家界林丰茶叶开发有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">品牌定位；品牌战略，；市场细分；2024百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Brand positioning; Brand strategy; Market segmentation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例以张家界林丰茶叶开发有限公司的品牌定位为主线，描述了林丰茶叶公司从选择茶叶市场进行创业，初入茶叶市场时如何应对市场竞争，如何细分市场进行品牌定位突围的农业企业创业历程。本文从供应端和消费端的困境，到行业内品牌竞争和潜在进入者的威胁，再到替代品如咖啡与新茶饮的冲击，深入探讨了茶叶行业的现状与挑战。结合STP理论，精准分析顾客需求、确定目标市场、明确品牌定位，从品牌名称的文学创意、包装设计的国潮文化以及品牌背后的责任与担当等方面分析林丰茶叶公司如何突破“有品类无品牌”的行业困境，在激烈的市场竞争中脱颖而出。本案例指出了当前茶叶企业所面临的行业困境，有助于学生了解品牌定位的相关方法，提高分析问题和解决问题的能力，也可为农业企业实施品牌战略提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case takes the brand positioning of Zhangjiajie Linfeng Tea Development Co., Ltd. as the main line, describes the entrepreneurial process of Linfeng Tea Company from choosing the tea market to start a business, how to deal with the market competition when it first entered the tea market, and how to break through the competition by brand positioning in market segments. This paper explores the current situation and challenges of the tea industry from the dilemma of the supply side and the consumption side, to the threat of brand competition and potential entrants in the industry, and to the impact of substitutes such as coffee and new tea. Combined with STP theory, the paper accurately analyzed customer demand, determined the target market, clarified the brand positioning, and analyzed how Linfeng Tea Company broke through the industry dilemma of &quot;category without brand&quot; and stood out in the fierce market competition from the aspects of literary creativity of brand name, national tide culture of packaging design and the responsibility and responsibility behind the brand. This case points out the current industry dilemma faced by tea enterprises, which is helpful to help students understand the relevant methods of brand positioning, improve the ability to analyze and solve problems, and also provide reference for agricultural enterprises to implement brand strategy.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》、《品牌营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">波特五力模型的内容及分析方法；消费者角色理论的相关内容；STP理论的内容及分析方法；品牌结构协同的内容及分析方法；品牌定位的分析方法、品牌拓展与品牌延伸的内容及分析方法。</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
